org.apache.ignite.plugin.extensions.communication

Interface MessageFactory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Extension

    public interface MessageFactory
extends Extension
    Factory for communication messages.

    A plugin can provide his own message factory as an extension if it uses any custom messages (all message must extend Message class).

    • Method Summary

      Methods

      Message create(byte type)
      Creates new message instance of provided type.

        @Nullable
Message create(byte type)
        Creates new message instance of provided type.

        This method should return null if provided message type is unknown to this factory.

        type - Message type.
        Returns:
        Message instance.
